Constants.Name: CommunityCommons.MergeMultiplePdfs_MaxAtOnce
Constants.Description:
Restricted to 10 files at once for Mendix Cloud v4 compatibility. If you need to merge more than 10 files increase the number here. Setting the value to <=0 means unlimited.

Note: We very strongly recommend to not increase the number for applications running in Mendix Cloud v4.

Constants.Name: TaskQueueHelpers.DeleteBatchSize
Constants.Description: The size of the batches during the clean up for ProcessedTasks. Keeping the higher value may causes potential memory issues.

Constants.Name: TaskQueueHelpers.TasksCompletedOlderThanHours
Constants.Description: The completed processed tasks which are older than this value in hours would be deleted during cleanup.

Constants.Name: TaskQueueHelpers.TasksNonCompletedOlderThanHours
Constants.Description: The NonCompleted tasks which are older than this value in hours would be deleted during cleanup.

Constants.Name: UnitTesting.FindJUnitTests
Constants.Description: Set this value to 'True' when you would like to include your available JUnit tests to be found and listed. Leave 'False' otherwise
